com.robopupu.api.mvp

Class ViewFragmentDelegate<T_Presenter extends Presenter,T_Fragment extends android.app.Fragment>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.robopupu.api.mvp.ViewFragmentDelegate<T_Presenter,T_Fragment>
  • Type Parameters:
    T_Presenter - The parametrised type of the Presenter.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Scopeable, PresentedView<T_Presenter>, View
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    FeatureViewFragmentDelegate

    public abstract class ViewFragmentDelegate<T_Presenter extends Presenter,T_Fragment extends android.app.Fragment>
extends java.lang.Object
implements View, PresentedView<T_Presenter>, Scopeable
    ViewFragmentDelegate provides an delegate class that can be used by concrete Fragment implementations which are not derived from ViewFragment.
